     C           *IN90     DOUEQ*ON
     C           K#ADH     REDPEAAGPL03                  90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           O4SKJY    ANDEQ*BLANK
      *
     C                     Z-ADDO4SYOS    WCT,I
     C                     Z-ADDO4KTSU    WDQ,I
